name: NUKA QUANTUM
description:
"Nuka-Cola Quantum was created in October 2076, with its subsequent inspections performed under the supervision of the Food and Drug Association, and was introduced in the fourth quarter of 2077 as a brand-new flavor of Nuka-Cola, with twice the calories, twice the carbohydrates, twice the caffeine and twice the taste. It was developed under the code name "Sea Lion", being their plant in Washington, D.C. the only facility to ever produce the beverage. Nuka-Cola Quantum was officially released to the public at the same time as the Great War, and so the soda is incredibly rare in the wasteland, with many bottles found in trucks that were shipping the product."

*CONTAINS 700mg OF CAFFEINE*
